metadata.name: Lonely
metadata.description:
Lonely is about a kid whose parents have mysteriously disappeared and is looking on yearningly as a Panda plays with his cubs , set in a neon lit city street  .

‘Doko’ collection is about an imaginary world ‘WHERE’ the only residents are animals and kids and the adults have mysteriously gone missing.

The collection brings forth the various interactions between them in this imaginary world.
